  05 May 2017; Barry Schwartz <sortsmill@crudfactory.com> -florist-2016.ebuild,
  -florist-2016-r1.ebuild, -florist-2016-r2.ebuild,
  -files/2016-r1/50Makefile.in.patch, -files/2016-r1/50c-posix.c.patch,
  -files/2016-r2/50build-multiple-ways.patch, -files/2016-r2/50c-posix.c.patch:
  Removal of the older florist ebuilds.

*florist-2016-r3 (05 May 2017)

  05 May 2017; Barry Schwartz <sortsmill@crudfactory.com>
  +florist-2016-r3.ebuild, +files/50c-posix.c.patch,
  +files/50florist-2016-gentoo-build.patch:
  A new florist ebuild that respects ADAFLAGS and CFLAGS and is more verbose.

  02 May 2017; Barry Schwartz <sortsmill@crudfactory.com>
  florist-2016-r2.ebuild:
  Extended a comment.

*florist-2016-r2 (02 May 2017)

  02 May 2017; Barry Schwartz <sortsmill@crudfactory.com> florist-2016.ebuild,
  florist-2016-r1.ebuild, +florist-2016-r2.ebuild,
  +files/2016-r2/50build-multiple-ways.patch, +files/2016-r2/50c-posix.c.patch:
  I fixed a bug that prevented building with threads support.
  Also I added a new ebuild that installs static, static-pic, and relocatable.

*florist-2016-r1 (01 May 2017)

  01 May 2017; Barry Schwartz <sortsmill@crudfactory.com>
  +florist-2016-r1.ebuild, +files/2016-r1/50Makefile.in.patch,
  +files/2016-r1/50c-posix.c.patch:
  A new ebuild that installs a shared libforest instead of static, and which
  fixes a minor bug.

*florist-2016 (19 Apr 2017)

  19 Apr 2017; Barry Schwartz <sortsmill@crudfactory.com>
  -florist-2007.0.ebuild, +florist-2016.ebuild:
  Bump version to florist 2016.

*florist-2007.0 (15 Aug 2014)

  15 Aug 2014; Barry Schwartz <sortsmill@crudfactory.com>
  +florist-2007.0.ebuild, +metadata.xml:
  Initial ebuild for sys-devel/gcc[ada]

